rong shocks, large shear, and fast cloud-cloud\ncollisions caused by the noncircular motion of the bar, result in a low SFE.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Nov 2022 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Dec 2022 16:00:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-25"}
