 can\nreduce the beam sweeping overhead by approximately 95%.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2022 03:58:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Nov 2022 07:55:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-01"}
