enness for the embedding of a partial frame into its free fame, and into its\ncongruence frame.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2022 09:59:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Mar 2023 17:50:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-20"}
