lanetary disks. Finally, we predict the existence of a sizable\npopulation of brown dwarf companions to low-mass stars and of a rising\npopulation of planetary-mass objects towards $\\approx 1\\,M_\\mathrm{Jup}$ around\nsolar-type stars. Improvements on current instrumentation will test these\npredictions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Nov 2022 22:25:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-14"}
