y, Martinize2 is used to convert\nthe entire I-TASSER protein template database as high-complexity benchmark and\nillustrate how the checks on input structure quality can safe guard\nhigh-throughput applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2022 11:23:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-05"}
